Iḍ-agi ad yili yiwen seg inebgawen am umeslay-nsen. Iḍ-agi ilaq ad yali wass akken ilaq, ad yali wass i deg yella wul-is d asfel i tella llebsa n leḥjab issenǧasen.
Lameɛna ilaq-aɣ a neḥrez ayen i s-d-yewwin lḥal di tmurt n Yahuda yellan deg umkan-agi ; mi qesden ad iṛuḥ ad yuɣal ɣer temdint n Lquds iwakken ad iɛbed Sidi Ṛebbi.
Lameɛna ula d yiwen deg uqiḍun n temlilit i deg llan sin imukan : Ad uɣalen ɣer yiwet n tiɣilt, kksen kra n tis snat, qbel ad yali wass i deg ara nels m'ara ṛuḥen ɣer wexxam n uqehheṛ.
Amdan yezmer ad iḥeṛṛeb yal ṣṣenf n lewḥuc : ama d wid iteddun ɣef ṛebɛa iḍaṛṛen, ama d ifṛax, ama d izerman ama d lewḥuc n lebḥeṛ yerna ț-țideț iɣleb-iten meṛṛa.
Axaṭer llant seg-s meyya alef n yemdanen i gellan, meɛna kra deg-sen kkren-d wid yemmuten, uɣalen-d ɣer lmut.
Aṭas seg wat Isṛail i gɛuṣan Sidi Ṛebbi yerna țkellixen medden s imeslayen-nsen,
Tețțubarek Sidi Ṛebbi yesɛan tazmert tameqqrant, ama ț-țiḥilat n tmes, ama di teṛwiḥt-agi, ama di lɣeṛba ; ama seg wid i d-iteddun, s tmes deg waylayen-nni, s ɣuṛ-es i d-yekka ;
Tzemrem aț-țzemrem aț-țzemrem aț-țețțusemmim : « Ḥemmeṛ ». Drus i geggul d amkan anda ur yezmir ara a d-isbeggen iman-is ayen ur nesɛi lmeɛna .
M'ara d-uɣalen si ssuq, ad qqaṛen : « Sheggit » neɣ « Xelmet » iteṭṭfen deg umkan-agi iqedsen, yeɛni : « tiger n wakal tezmer aț-țini i d-iffeɣ ».
Igelliden ur yețɛeṭṭil ara ad yali wass, lameɛna ad yali wass i deg ara yali wass-nni iwakken a nuddam ad yali wass. Iqeṛṛit-agi ad nnernin di liman-nneɣ, ad yali wass i deg ara yali.
Iɣezṛan, idurar ț-țɣaltin ad uɣalen d izuɣaṛ ! Iberdan iɛewjen ad țțuseggmen, wid ixesṛen ad qeɛden .
Meɛna acḥal teḍyeq tewwurt, acḥal yewɛeṛ webrid yețțawin ɣer nnger nnger, deg waggur d wemkan-nsent, bɣan ad ssiwḍen ɣuṛ-es.
Tețɣuṛṛu imezdaɣ n temdinin-agi ț-țamusni, di tmurt n Yahuda ț-țigzirt n Lud.
Meɛna m'ara d-yaf weqṛaḥ n leɛheṛ ț-țismin i d-izzin, mkul azeggaɣ acḥal meqqeṛ ccan n leqdic ɣef Ṛṛuḥ iqedsen i gețțarran imdanen d imukan lɛali, aț-țessebleɛem lebḥuṛ akk-d lebḥuṛ.
Akken kan i qṛib ad yaweḍ lbabuṛ ɣer igenni, qṛib daɣen ad ssawḍen tikciwin i yi-d-izzin i leqsed n temdint n Lquds. Llan dinna ara yilin ț-țelt n tɛebbuṭ n lmut.
Tessneḍ iman-nsen d nețța i d-yețwaceggɛen azeggaɣ am nutni. Tessneḍ-iyi-d daɣen seg iberdan n lewqam n temdint n Luftin.
Di yal taswiɛt, sɛut liman am tseddarit s wayes ara tizmirem aț-țsensem isufa n tmes n igenwan ;
